<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL29">
<l>ūrilēṉ kāṇi yillai yuṟavumaṟ ṟoruva rillai</l>
<l>pārilniṉ pāta mūlam paṟṟilēṉ parama mūrtti</l>
<l>kāroḷi vaṇṇa ṉē kaṇṇaṉē kataṟu kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>āruḷar kaḷaik kaṇṇammā varaṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not have a town; I do not have lands; I do not have relatives or anyone else;</l>
<l>I have not held on to Your feet on [this] earth, O Supreme Being!</l>
<l>O shiny cloud-hued [Lord]! (My) Kṛṣṇa! I am wailing [in despair]!</l>
<l>O Master! What [other] lord is there?</l>
<l>O Lord! O You of the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
